{"tid":1192960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，加油。","createTime":"2019-06-08T16:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:45:40.000Z","uid":202170,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9955a714ef3151e2211d5602b39eed992c056ae2","tid":1192960,"uid":202170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"而家大學year 1，魚蛋革命個陣仲細，對政治不聞不問，但記得個陣去完海洋公園，已經好夜，見到金鐘仲有好多人嘅情景真係好震撼。<br />\n<br />\n而家諗返起覺得好羞愧。中學好少講呢啲，身邊同學都只係圍威喂，打打鬧鬧過一日。升咗上大學，呢一年先真係留意多咗時事，好想守護呢個屬於香港人嘅土地。<br />\n<br />\n今日見到有啲師弟妹喺ig要啲人出嚟真係好撚感動，原來以為我呢啲band 2學校啲人唔會留意，但原來都有好多人會參與。<br />\n<br />\n講唔出啲咩大道理，只係想講聲加油。<br />\n希望可以見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ee30453f7540b0fcbf17519e59dd9ac38ff104","tid":1192960,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f993c3e40dd48a0c43b6ea64b8b782d3365837","tid":1192960,"uid":202170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"1f19ebc6af0e57949601c64d218ba47ca519a625","tid":1192960,"uid":202170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"db7ccfa809647d0c29234283a0d762805d33a2e0","tid":1192960,"uid":202170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"Btw 記得準備乾糧 水 毛巾 純色衫"}]}